                    disabilities.</a></li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Our Covid-19 Response</a></li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Report a neighbourhood
                    concern</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="col-6 col-md-2 mb-3">
              <h5>Hosting</h5>
              <ul class="nav flex-column">
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Airbnb your Home</a></li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Aircover for hosts</a></li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Explore Hosting Resources</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Visit your community forum</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">How to host responsibly.</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="col-6 col-md-2 mb-3">
              <h5>Airbnb</h5>
              <ul class="nav flex-column">
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Newsroom</a></li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Learn about new features.</a>
                </li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Learn from our founders</a></li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Careers</a></li>
                <li class="nav-items mb-2"><a href="#" class="nav-link p-0 text-muted">Investors</a></li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-5 offset-md-1 mb-3">
              <form>
                <h5>Subscribe to our Airbnbnews.</h5>
                <p>Monthly digest of what's new and exciting from us.</p>
                <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row w-100 gap-2">
                  <label for="newsletter1" class="visually-hidden">Email address</label>
                  <input id="newsletter1" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Email address">
                  <button class="btn btn-danger" type="button">Subscribe</button>
                </div>
              </form>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-sm-row justify-content-between py-4 my-4 border-top">
            <p>&copy; 2022 Airbnb,Inc .Privacy .Terms .Sitemap .Company Details.</p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled d-flex">
              <li class="ms-3"><a class="link-dark" href="#"><svg class="bi" width="24" height="24"><i
                      class="fa-sharp fa-solid fa-globe"></i> </svg></a></li>
              <li class="ms-3"><a class="link-dark" href="#"><svg class="bi" width="24" height="24"> <i
